{
  "texts": [
    "Model (C) adds a de-tection head for dynamic object supervision, achieving lim-ited gain (+0.9 mIoU on dynamic objects) due to the lackof direct feature-level injection.",
    "In contrast, model (D) in-tegrates QueryAgg, which directly injects dynamic objectfeatures into the corresponding voxel regions.",
    "This targetedaggregation improves performance on dynamic objects by+2.7 mIoU compared to (B) and increases overall mIoUto 41.90, while maintaining performance on static objects.Moreover, DuOcc surpasses the previous real-time state-of-the-art GSD-Occ [8] across most object classes, demon-strating the effectiveness of our framework.",
